sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant AGW as API Gateway
    participant API as API Lambda
    participant S3in as S3 (input)
    participant DDB as DynamoDB
    participant EB as EventBridge
    participant DP as Document Processor
    participant BDA
    participant S3out as S3 (output)
    participant RP as Result Processor
    participant SQS
    participant MP as Metrics Processor
    participant S3m as S3 (metrics, Parquet)

    C->>AGW: POST /v1/documents
    AGW->>API: invoke
    API->>S3in: put object
    API->>DDB: write metadata
    API-->>C: 202 job_id
    S3in->>EB: ObjectCreated
    EB->>DP: invoke
    DP->>BDA: InvokeDataAutomationAsync
    BDA->>S3out: write result
    S3out->>EB: ObjectCreated
    EB->>RP: invoke
    RP->>DDB: update status + fields
    RP->>SQS: emit metrics
    SQS->>MP: invoke
    MP->>S3m: write Parquet